PropertyValue.String: Reads information on the header data of production order confirmations.
Reads information available on the header data of existing production order confirmations. You can use the standard OData system query options to refine your request.
Reads information on the header data of a single production order confirmation.
Reads the information for a specific production order confirmation that you specify using the confirmation group and the confirmation count.
Reads the material document for goods movements.
Reads information available on the material document items of existing confirmations. You can use the standard OData system query options to refine your request.
Reads information on a single material document for goods movements.

Reads the information of a single material document item that you specify using the confirmation group number, the confirmation count, the number of the material document, the item in the material document, and the material document year.
Reads the batch characteristics in material documents for goods movements.
Reads information available on the batch characteristics in material document items of existing confirmations. You can use the standard OData system query options to refine your request.
Reads information on a single batch characteristic in a material document for goods movements.

Reads the information on a single batch characteristic in a material document item that you specify using the confirmation group, the confirmation count,the material document number, the item in the material document, the material document year, the plant, the material, the batch, and the internal ID of the batch characteristic.
Creates a new production order confirmation.

Creates the header data for a new production order confirmation using the properties you provide. If desired, a material document for goods movement can be created together with the confirmation as well.
Reads the header data of a production order confirmation together with the corresponding material documents for goods movements.

Reads the header data of a single production order confirmation that you specify using the confirmation group and confirmation count. The response includes the material documents for goods movements belonging to the confirmation.
Reads the material document for goods movements together with the corresponding batch characteristics.

Reads a material document for goods movements that you specify using the confirmation group, the confirmation count, the material document number, the materialdocument item number, and the material document year. The response includes the batch characteristics belonging to the material document.

Annotation.String: Cancels a production order confirmation that you specify using the confirmation group and confirmation count.
Fetches proposal data for quantities, work activities, dates and times, and personnel data for confirmations.
Fetches proposal data of a confirmation that you specify using the necessary properties depending on the type of confirmation.
Fetches proposal data for goods movements of a confirmation.
Fetches proposal data for goods movements of a confirmation that you specify using the necessary properties depending on the type of confirmation.
